---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';
import DownloadSection from '@/components/DownloadSection';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="다운로드 - IMAS">
  <!-- Header -->
  <section class="border-b border-border/40 py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 text-center">
      <Badge variant="outline" className="mb-4 text-[#4a9eff] border-[#4a9eff]/40">Download</Badge>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-5xl">다운로드</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-muted-foreground">
        최신 버전의 IMAS를 다운로드하세요
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Download Content -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
      <DownloadSection client:load />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SmartScreen Guide -->
  <section class="border-t border-border/40 py-20 bg-muted/30">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <Badge variant="outline" className="mb-4 border-amber-500/40 bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-600">
          실행 시 안내
        </Badge>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold md:text-4xl">
          Windows SmartScreen 경고가 뜰 때
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-muted-foreground">
          다운로드 후 <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-muted text-sm">IMAS.exe</code> 실행 시
          <strong>"Windows의 PC 보호"</strong> 경고가 표시될 수 있습니다.
          아래 순서대로 진행해주세요.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border/60 bg-background p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#4a9eff] text-white font-bold text-sm">1</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">"추가 정보" 클릭</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-border/40">
            <img src={`${base}images/smartscreen-1.png`} alt="SmartScreen 경고 1단계" class="w-full h-auto" />
            <div
              class="absolute pointer-events-none rounded"
              style="left: 3.5%; top: 20.5%; width: 13%; height: 5.5%; border: 3px solid #ef4444; box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(239,68,68,0.4);"
              aria-hidden="true"
            ></div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            파란색 경고 화면에서 좌측의 <strong>"추가 정보"</strong> 링크를 클릭합니다.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border/60 bg-background p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#4a9eff] text-white font-bold text-sm">2</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">"실행" 버튼 클릭</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-border/40">
            <img src={`${base}images/smartscreen-2.png`} alt="SmartScreen 경고 2단계" class="w-full h-auto" />
            <div
              class="absolute pointer-events-none rounded"
              style="left: 63%; top: 87%; width: 13%; height: 8%; border: 3px solid #ef4444; box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(239,68,68,0.4);"
              aria-hidden="true"
            ></div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            새로 나타난 <strong>"실행"</strong> 버튼을 클릭하면 IMAS가 정상적으로 실행됩니다.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 rounded-lg border border-border/40 bg-background/50 p-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-foreground">왜 이 경고가 뜨나요?</strong>
          현재 IMAS는 코드 서명 인증서 적용 전이라 Microsoft SmartScreen이 일시적으로 차단합니다.
          <span class="text-foreground">안전한 소프트웨어이며</span>, 인증서 적용 후에는 경고가 나타나지 않습니다.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
